display_long_description:
Double Taggers V2 is a Gorilla Tag fan game that mixes fast movement with goofy fun. Jump, climb, and swing your way through creative maps designed to keep you moving and laughing at the same time. Every match is about speed, skill, and silly moments with friends as you try to tag or escape.

Whether you’re running across rooftops, climbing trees, or pulling off crazy jumps, the game keeps the action fast and funny. The simple controls make it easy to pick up, but the movement feels smooth and rewarding once you get the hang of it. Play casually for laughs, or go all out to prove who’s the fastest swifter in the lobby.

With its mix of playful maps, quick rounds, and nonstop energy, Double Taggers V2 is all about making every tag exciting—and every fail hilarious.
